Label: util_TNC_SINGLE_Cost
Expression: @np.maximum(TNC_single_baseFare + odt_skims['HOV2_DIST'] * TNC_single_costPerMile + odt_skims['HOV2_TIME'] * TNC_single_costPerMinute, TNC_single_costMinimum) * 100 * df.ivot

Label: util_TNC_SHARED_Cost
Expression: @np.maximum(TNC_shared_baseFare + odt_skims['HOV2_DIST'] * TNC_shared_costPerMile + odt_skims['HOV2_TIME'] * TNC_shared_costPerMinute, TNC_shared_costMinimum) * 100 * df.ivot
